#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag1.6:4.1"
msgid "1.6. Sītavaniyattheragāthā"
msgstr "1.6. Sītavaniya"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc6"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts6"></a>
msgctxt "thag1.6:5.1"
msgid "“Yo sītavanaṃ upagā bhikkhu,"
msgstr "The monk who went to Sītavana is solitary,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.6:5.2"
msgid "Eko santusito samāhitatto;"
msgstr "content and serene,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.6:5.3"
msgid "Vijitāvī apetalomahaṃso,"
msgstr "victorious, with goosebumps vanished,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.6:5.4"
msgid "Rakkhaṃ kāyagatāsatiṃ dhitimā”ti."
msgstr "guarding mindfulness of the body, resolute."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "thag1.6:6.1"
msgid "Itthaṃ sudaṃ āyasmā sītavaniyo thero gāthaṃ abhāsitthāti."
msgstr ""
"It was thus that this verse was recited by the senior venerable Sītavaniya."
